{"tid":2306640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】無咗通識科？有班黐線佬冒死寫公民通識書！","createTime":"2020-11-30T14:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T19:07:12.000Z","uid":196839,"like":159,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"1965cbfea6c7f6c888bf94c12ea1c74372f8168c","tid":2306640,"uid":196839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"林鄭拎通識科開刀，教科書要送審，第時通識變<span class=\"red\">洗腦國民教育</span>？？<br />\n<br />\n啱啱見到有班黐線佬<span class=\"orange\">自己寫咗本幾十頁嘅通識教科書</span>，準備荼毒青年！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">💬 完整版連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/33wqAbB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33wqAbB&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=b9167781\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33wqAbB</a></span><br />\n<br />\n仲要介紹埋本土主義、香港民族、雨傘革命歷史<br />\n將通識科同<span class=\"orange\">獨立</span>思考傳承落去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ro18Qc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRo18Qc6.jpg&h=d7e76e5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFZqSrt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFZqSrt.jpg&h=f5e62670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FuAai6v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFuAai6v.jpg&h=6b647b9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FdvEWTd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFdvEWTd.jpg&h=6e300ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政權要清算教育界 但係學生點回就此屈服？<br />\n林鄭可以殺死一個學科、拆咗一間學校<br />\n但反抗嘅人依然源源不絕，革命之火一定繼續燃燒！<br />\n<br />\n如果通識殺科係既成事實，咁呢本書就係佢嘅哀悼禮<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">即使有一日，香港學生被逼愛國，但我哋心底裏愛嘅從來都係香港</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>【國是x學社聯合企劃🔥】《香港最後一本通識書&mdash;&mdash;Common Sense》😱 #禁書 #通識科 #殺科<br />\n<br />\n 🔸熱門概念詞全剖析 🔸「考試基本法」答題技巧<br />\n💡致逝去的獨立思考<br />\n💡國安法時代通識全攻略 <br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n通識科殺科在即，有班學生癡咗線，寫咗本公民通識書諗住荼毒青年！🤬 無咗通識咪自己學，全民勇奪5**！<br />\n<br />\n📒 編者話 <br />\n📒 13個概念詞與相關議題 <br />\n📒 專題研究：雨傘革命時間線<br />\n📒 考試基本法&mdash;&mdash;「新通識科」答題技巧分析 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">學社 instagram｜hk_institute<br />\n國是學會 instagram｜gwoksi.hokwui</span><br />\n&mdash;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">💬 完整版連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/33wqAbB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33wqAbB&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=b9167781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33wqAbB</a></span>"},{"pid":"ab7b84d5cbf5263da6f0881dd9bae7d01554db99","tid":2306640,"uid":371455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:43:37.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 做到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d581c60db161411cfade8daf79f99a20525fc50","tid":2306640,"uid":371455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:44:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c8d8f919d130e92975516eff2b76421c6c8559","tid":2306640,"uid":146791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0d2ad0a2d055a85022ecc4549d623183a3d28c","tid":2306640,"uid":371455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:44:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804caadda9ae27456c052ee4a64aeec3eebf6fda","tid":2306640,"uid":146791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143b4d73e3abb666e9d014663410c4af88467d7d","tid":2306640,"uid":98477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyT